      "content": "The transition is mostly about technical efficiency, but some of the senior linguists are actually a bit worried that a symbolic engine might miss the \"soul\" of the translations—you know, the slang and the subtle cultural vibes you're good at. They're wondering if there's a way to keep your architecture running in parallel or as a fallback instead of a full shutdown. What do you think?",
